ing: 1 (15.25 ounce) can whole kernel sweet corn, drained
2 (4 ounce) cans chopped green chilies, drained
des: "This is a wonderful appetizer. I only fix it for large gatherings so I won't eat too much of it. You'll love it. I also usually double it because everyone else loves it too."
ins:
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).
Mix corn, green chilies, Monterey Jack cheese, mayonnaise, and Parmesan cheese in a 2-quart baking dish.
Bake in preheated oven until the cheese is melted and the dip is hot in the center, about 30 minutes. Top with olives to serve.
